name: Honey Hoover
description:
A beehive has fallen to the ground. You're an ant trying to collect honey without getting detected by the bees. More ants appear as you eat honey. Don't step on the larva, or it will alert the bees!

Honey Hoover was conceived of by Caleb Carney and created with the help of Ivan Craddock and ida kenna.

Caleb - project lead, art, game programming

Ivan - game programming

ida - game programming
